column14: The choices I made in the game were the typical choices I would make when using social media apps such as Facebook. I thought that my choices were safe enough, particularly in not removing the tagged photo by my friend and in choosing a photo to post. The game made me realize that in using social media, it is best to not reveal any information as simple tags or photo posts could reveal a lot of information that I do not intend to be known by strangers.
